thread.title: Nemetschek Vectorworks and BIMobject sign cooperation agreement
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Nemetschek Vectorworks and BIMobject sign cooperation agreement | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Nemetschek Vectorworks and BIMobject sign cooperation agreement
text:
Sept 1 Bimobject AB :
* Nemetschek Vectorworks and BIMobject sign cooperation agreement
* Nemetschek Vectorworks and BIMobject will support each other's BIM technology in order to better accommodate needs of AEC (architecture, engineering and construction) industry
Source text for Eikon:
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
